Had a really awesome time out in North Carolina this past weekend competing at the @united.scoot @ddasc competition! Big congratulations to @chris_beyrent for taking home 2nd place and @tj_dolin for taking 3rd! You guys crushed it! Blessed to take home 1st place and get the Golden Ticket to the @isfworldscooterchampionships in Australia! Stoked to go to Aus 🇦🇺! Big thank you to @scooter_zone and @raymondwarnerdotcom for always taking care of me and making sure I’m riding smooth! Big thank you to @united.scoot for putting on this comp series and @ddasc / @thescooterfarm for the hospitality! 🤝🏻🙏🏻
